USAGE

perl collect_pdf.pl [folder_template]

has to be run in a directory that contains folders with png files
resulted from different models. 

folder_template is the optional argument (default is "*") to plot only figures from folders whose names begin with this string.

EXAMPLE 

perl collect_pdf.pl tit

It collects all png figures made by HACOL from
all subdirectories tit*/ in the current folder
in one latex-file (all_figures.tex) 
which is compiled into PDF.

Needs:
 collect_pdf.pl
 begin.tex
 end.tex
